===more:Ayatollah Khomeini proposed that, “America is the number-one enemy of the deprived and oppressed people of the world.  There is no crime America will not commit in order to maintain its political, economic, cultural, and military domination.”  Examine this statement.  Discuss the relationship between the United States and the Islamic world.  Why is it often so troubled? 
